WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:05.000
[Agent] Hello, UW IT Service Desk. This is Alex. How can I help you today?

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:08.000
[user] Hi, I'm having trouble accessing my email.

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:12.000
[Agent] I'd be happy to help. Can I get your NetID to verify your account?

00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:15.000
[user] Sure, it's student123.

00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:22.000
[Agent] Thank you. For security, I'll need to verify your identity using Zoom. Can you start a Zoom call with me?

00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:25.000
[user] Yes, I can do that.

00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:35.000
[Agent] Great. Now that I've verified your identity, let me check your email settings. It looks like your password expired. I'll walk you through resetting it.

00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:40.000
[Agent] Go to myuw.uw.edu and click on the password reset link. Follow the prompts to create a new password.

00:00:40.500 --> 00:00:43.000
[user] Okay, I'm doing that now.

00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:48.000
[Agent] Make sure your password is at least 12 characters with uppercase, lowercase, and numbers.

00:00:48.500 --> 00:00:51.000
[user] Done! I can access my email now.

00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:55.000
[Agent] Excellent! Is there anything else I can help you with today?

00:00:55.500 --> 00:00:57.000
[user] No, that's all. Thank you!

00:00:57.500 --> 00:01:00.000
[Agent] You're welcome. Have a great day!
